WEBVTT

00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:09.550
The governing body is pleased to present the following video for your enjoyment.

00:00:09.550 --> 00:00:16.589
This film uses Bible principles to assist ones both in choosing a good marriage mate

00:00:16.589 --> 00:00:21.390
and in showing true love to each other once married.

00:00:21.390 --> 00:00:28.589
We realize that throughout the world there are many unique customs with regard to courtship.

00:00:28.589 --> 00:00:34.189
In this video is not intended to endorse or discount any of those.

00:00:34.189 --> 00:00:42.829
Instead, please focus on the scriptural principles that will apply equally in all cultures.

00:00:42.829 --> 00:00:46.509
I am now pleased to introduce the video.

00:00:46.509 --> 00:00:48.990
What is true love?
